profile:
Erdem Excavating was established in Victoria, BC in 2008 with the vision of becoming an innovative, quality based, industry contender. Our team is comprised of qualified and experienced individuals who value honesty, integrity, safety and environmental responsibility.

Erdem Excavating is constantly evolving to suit the unique requirements of each client, whether commercial or residential. The diversity of our skill set enables us to complete even the most challenging of projects in a timely, cost effective and professional manner. Erdem Excavating is fully insured and WCB certified.
